author: Rob Braxman Tech
description:
This is a practical guide explaining the potential risks of third party apps on a phone. Just to eliminate the threats of Apple and Google in the equation, this video will focus solely on a de-Googled phones which will not have anything from Google secretly embedded in it. But even in this case, lack of knowledge will result in a lot of dangerous exfiltration of your private data. Fortunately this is an aspect of phone use that has solutions.
